---
title: Easy Honey Harissa Lamb with Roasted Root Veggie Toss & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Harissa, the chilli-based condiment originating from North Africa varies in heat from mild to firey. Our version is definitely on the
mild side, with a gentle heat plus herby spices. It's the ideal sauce to complement lamb, and with a hearty roast veggie toss plus a
side of creamy yoghurt, there's a burst of flavour in every bite!

*Keep an eye out... Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be slightly different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
